metadata.name: 2D Mansion #976
metadata.description:
A mansion generator to crash real estate prices.

Press 'n' or click on the sun to cycle day/night, 's' toggle the canvas resizing and allows to zoom or take a picture at full resolution.

Guest has 7 different values (Two can only happen at a certain moon phase) and there are 4 different materials.

metadata.name: Mandatory hijab #79
metadata.description:

This NFT is a protest movement against the mandatory hijab, which causes the death of women in many countries of the world

metadata.name: Unsolicited abstraction of modern times #8
metadata.description:
This piece is an abstraction and a reflection on the last era, on all that we have built and become. Are we proud of it or has it just been the result of iterating through the days? Since the technology boom, we have experienced great improvements, but perhaps also massive ...mistakes?‚Ä®‚Ä®

Inspired by textbooks of the 80s, with elements that remind us of industry, technology, networks and systems, "Unsolicited abstraction of modern times" invites us to question our work to date. Has everything really changed?

unknowable 2022




Usage:
press [s] - save pixels (png)
press [p] - save vectors (svg)
